# AI Context Configuration - error/

## Directory Purpose
Error detection and analysis system with plugin architecture.

## AI Indexing Priority
PRIORITY: HIGH
Critical quality assurance system - should be indexed for error-related tasks.

## Scope
ACTIVE_CODE - Production error detection and plugin management.

## Key Components
- engine/ - Error engine, state machine, plugin manager
- plugins/ - Detection plugins for various languages and tools
- shared/utils/ - Hashing, time utilities, JSONL manager

## Plugin Architecture
Each plugin:
- Has manifest.json with metadata
- Implements parse() for detection
- Optionally implements fix() for auto-remediation
- Uses file hash caching for incremental detection

## Import Pattern
from error.engine.error_engine import ErrorEngine
from error.engine.plugin_manager import PluginManager
from error.plugins.python_ruff.plugin import parse

## When to Use This Section
- Adding error detection features
- Creating new detection plugins
- Modifying error engine logic
- Integration with core pipeline

